# Lab 01: Configure AAA Authentication on Cisco Routers

## ðŸŽ¯ Objective

â€¢  Configure a local user account on R1 and configure authenticate on the console and vty lines using local AAA. (Task 1)
â€¢  Verify local AAA authentication from the R1 console and the PC-A client. (Task 2)
â€¢  Configure server-based AAA authentication using TACACS+. (Task 3)
